### Billing Engine – HTTP Requests
### Works with: IntelliJ HTTP Client  |  VS Code REST Client (humao.rest-client)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billing

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 1. PREMIUM SCHEDULE
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Quarterly policy – 4 instalments
GET {{baseUrl}}/policies/POL-1001/premium-schedule
Accept: application/json

###

### Monthly policy – 12 instalments
GET {{baseUrl}}/policies/POL-1002/premium-schedule
Accept: application/json

###

### Biannual policy – 2 instalments
GET {{baseUrl}}/policies/POL-1003/premium-schedule
Accept: application/json

###

### Unknown policy → 404
GET {{baseUrl}}/policies/POL-UNKNOWN/premium-schedule
Accept: application/json

###

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 2. RECORD PAYMENT ATTEMPT
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Successful payment (token does NOT end in 'fail')
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/attempts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "policyId":           "POL-1001",
  "amount":             320.00,
  "paymentMethodToken": "tok_visa_4242",
  "idempotencyKey":     "idem-001"
}

###

### Failed payment (token ends in 'fail')
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/attempts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "policyId":           "POL-1002",
  "amount":             145.50,
  "paymentMethodToken": "tok_card_fail",
  "idempotencyKey":     "idem-002"
}

###

### Validation error – blank policyId → 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/attempts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "policyId":           "",
  "amount":             320.00,
  "paymentMethodToken": "tok_test"
}

###

### Validation error – zero amount → 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/attempts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "policyId":           "POL-1001",
  "amount":             0,
  "paymentMethodToken": "tok_test"
}

###

### Unknown policy → 404
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/attempts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "policyId":           "POL-9999",
  "amount":             100.00,
  "paymentMethodToken": "tok_visa"
}

###

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 3. DELINQUENT POLICIES
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### List all delinquent policies
GET {{baseUrl}}/policies/delinquent
Accept: application/json

###

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 4. TRIGGER RETRY
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Retry for POL-1001  (run AFTER a failed attempt above to see back-off)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/retry/POL-1001

###

### Retry for POL-1002
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/retry/POL-1002

###

### Retry for POL-1003
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/retry/POL-1003

###

### Unknown policy → 404
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/retry/POL-9999

###
